{"tid":851177,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【左手交右手，留名等撻訂】瑧蓺開放式906.5萬售 呎價4.1萬貴絕全港","createTime":"2018-10-07T02:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T04:04:42.000Z","uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"119279c03ede93cce38cfcbeee82c7e5ab6bbace","tid":851177,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:58:26.000Z","msg":"市區劏房再次破頂，全港最貴開放式戶誕生。新世界發展旗下西營盤瑧蓺頂層33樓J室，實用面積221方呎，最新以906.5萬元成交，呎價高達41,018元，料成為全港最貴開放式單位成交。發展商指，項目累售245伙，套現近22億元，全盤尚餘最後5伙單位待售。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，對上一伙最貴開放式戶為同區由九建發展的63 Pokfulam，今年4月時1座27樓E室，實用面積209方呎的開放式單位，以836.3萬元成交，呎價40,014元。<br />\n<br />\n記者 陳寶恩<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181006/58765158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58765158&d=VXAYx0S8Fq2ve3j0i6Iwn8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=4841cff5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58765158&h=200bc117\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181006/58765158</a>"},{"pid":"b3f8e7faf3aa15dc3af4de99b840ab090501cb7e","tid":851177,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"200尺9m都戇鳩鳩 太古城低層都買到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa46c1f4303d5c2fd890d447dcd7381c61acfe20","tid":851177,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3f8e7faf3aa15dc3af4de99b840ab090501cb7e","tid":851177,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"200尺9m都戇鳩鳩 太古城低層都買到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:03:15.000Z","msg":"等睇撻訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427231b21bca08d6ea7aced389cb543745eedb07","tid":851177,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"4萬蚊呎200呎劏房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錢嘅人話你on9, 真有錢嘅當係on9"},{"pid":"90cf05cea3752a1b66f8fcf6efe3040993b2b067","tid":851177,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"九百幾萬買間劏房，真係黐撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1566789e20f7b793f5ed4ff325642e4944c0af45","tid":851177,"uid":125261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"Wait... 聽落九百萬買二百幾呎係痴九線，但如果同一個單位租到兩萬幾，條數又唔同計法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【西營盤南區呎租價】瑧蓺227呎開放戶 呎租撲百元 (17:10)<br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2018年10月4日<br />\n<br />\n港島新派迷你戶的租務市道向來有價有市，近期新入伙的西營盤瑧蓺，就有開放戶以實呎撲100元租出，媲美南區豪宅呎租。<br />\n <br />\n美聯首席助理聯席董事謝錦成表示，上述瑧蓺高層K室，屬實用227方呎開放式戶，獲外藉客以約2.2萬元承租，實呎租金97元，以業主去年購入價690.9萬元購入價計，享租金回報率3.8厘。瑧蓺另一低層實用213方呎D室，日前亦以實呎租金82元租出。<br />\n <br />\n樓盤現時在市場約有23個單位放租，當中開放式戶佔約17個，實呎叫租由89至120元水平不等，而開放式戶月租則由1.9萬至2.4萬元不等。"}]}